@wp.kernel
def expr_bzsvvp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = float(0.0)
    v2 = float(1.0)
    tmp = float(0.0)
    v0 = wp.exp((wp.sin(tmp + 0.53) - wp.exp(v2 + 0.16)))
    v2 = (wp.abs((tmp + 0.91 - v0 + 0.71)) + wp.abs(wp.cos(tmp + 0.91)))
    v2 = (((tmp + 0.92 + tmp + 0.48) - wp.sin(tmp + 0.63)) + (wp.sin(v2 + 0.43) + (v0 + 0.1 - v1 + 0.05)))
    v2 = (v0 * wp.sin((v1 + 0.39 * v1 + 0.78)))
    v0 = wp.cos((v2 - tmp))
    v0 = 0.72
    v2 = tmp
    tmp = ((v0 + wp.abs(v0 + 0.06)) / tmp)
    data[tid] = v0
